to which the proposed policy belongs. This problem finds\npotential applications in cognitive radio networks, multi-channel communication\nsystems, multi-agent systems, web search and advertising, and social networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2009 00:50:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Dec 2009 17:26:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2010 18:04:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
